#1. Start up MonoDevelop, click New... just below the Solutions heading, and click on the .NET
category in the Other section in the pane on the left. Click the Console Project icon in the
Templates pane and click Next. Change the Project Name to whatever name you want to call the
project, set the location where you'd like the project to be saved, and click Create.

File -> New -> Solution -> C# -> Console Project 

#2. Install Microsoft XNA
    Install Monogame
    
